text: Thank you for contacting Amazon Customer Service.
How may I help you today?
"Hi , I ordered a heater and it was damaged"
Can you verify your name and billing address so I can look that up?
"Great, one moment while I look up your order history. "
I have located your order and can provide a refund to the card you paid with.
"To begin, I will need the card number and expiration date"
"Next, I will need the CSV number from that card. "
"Thank you, give me a moment while I enter that information. "
You should be seeing your refund in 3-7 business days
"In the meantime, is there anything else I can help you with?"
"No That was it , Thank you so much for the good service"
Would you like to participate in a survey?
"Thank you, the survey link will be sent to your email."
Thank you and you have a great day !
